  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hôtel Nendaz 4 Vallées &amp; Spa is available on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Fuel up for the day at the varied breakfast buffet which includes various sweet and savoury options.</p>
<p>Each evening you can enjoy a three-course evening meal with two choices, in the modern Le Clos des Cimes restaurant. If you fancy a treat, you can also dine in the à la carte Le Carnotzet l'Aigle restaurant, which serves Swiss specialities including fondue and raclette.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
