  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hôtel Nendaz 4 Vallées &amp; Spa provides a luxurious and comfortable stay in the Swiss Alps. Its convenient location offers easy access to the walking routes and village centre, where you can find a variety of shops, bars, and restaurants. With cosy rooms, delicious local food and an extensive wellness area, this is a great choice for your next walking holiday.</p>
<h2>Cosy accommodation</h2>
<p>Each room at the Hôtel Nendaz 4 Vallées &amp; Spa is furnished in a traditional yet modern Valasian style with warm wood, slate and cosy furnishings than continue throughout the hotel. When you return from a day of adventures, sit back and relax with an aperitif in the bar area or take some time to rejuvenate in the extensive wellness area.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>If you fancy a day of relaxation or want to soothe your muscles after a day of exploring, the extensive Spa des Bisses is just the place. Relax in the various saunas, steam bath or ice cave or for incredible views of the mountains, head to the outdoor pool and terrace. For a real treat, book in for a massage or treatment (payable locally).</p>
<h2>Delicious food and drink</h2>
<p>Start your day at the varied breakfast buffet which includes a variety of sweet and savoury options and when you return from a day of exploring the bisses, forests and mountain trails, you can enjoy a three-course evening meal. If you want to treat yourself to an authentic Swiss meal, Le Carnotzet l'Aigle serves Swiss specialities including raclette, fondue and Valasian dishes.</p>]]></description>
