  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spa &amp; wellness facilities</strong></p>
<p>The 2,200-square-metre Spa des Bisses is a haven of relaxation, open every day from around 10am - 8pm. Children under 16 are allowed in the spa before 6pm and must be accompanied by an adult, after 6pm it's adults-only. Facilities include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Spa area with saunas, steam room, floatation basin, cold water bath, Kneipp circuit and panoramic relaxation room</li>
<li>Outdoor swimming pool, whirlpool and terrace with sun loungers</li>
<li>Children's area with small pool, fountains and games</li>
<li>Massages and beauty treatments (payable locally)</li>
<li>Fitness room</li>
<li>Spa towels are available from the spa reception</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Additional facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Bar, lounge and à la carte restaurant</li>
<li>Cigar Room</li>
<li>Underground parking (entry code is required)</li>
<li>Funicular (runs until around midnight)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Family facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Children's playroom</li>
<li>Children's pool area</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
