  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>50 metres to the Tracouet gondola station</li>
<li>There is a funicular at the back of the hotel to take you to the Tracouet gondola station</li>
<li>180 metres to the nearest supermarket and pharmacy</li>
<li>On arrival into Nendaz, stay on the bus until the final stop at Nendaz Telecabin. You can then head slightly uphill past the gondola station for the funicular down to the hotel</li>
</ul>]]></locationDescription>
